name: Tourism's Tiny Impact
title: Least Profitable Tourism Sector
description: In 2019, Guinea-Bissau's international tourism receipts for passenger transport were just $19,999.99, highlighting a minimal contribution to the economy.

name: Food First
title: High Dependency on Food Imports
description: In 2018, food imports constituted 41.71% of Guinea-Bissau's merchandise imports, indicating a significant reliance on external food sources.

name: Manufacturing Mirage
title: Negligible Manufacturing Exports
description: In 2015, manufacturing exports made up a mere 0.00009% of Guinea-Bissau's merchandise exports, showing a lack of industrial export activity.
